# Task tracker

**Single source of truth for progress across all slices.** Every worker agent updates this file. Primary session rebalances tasks from here.

Status legend: `[ ]` not started · `[~]` in progress · `[x]` done · `[!]` blocked

Format for in-progress / done / blocked entries:
`- [~|x|!] YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MM <agent-id> — what you're doing / did / why blocked`

